006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.binding.metaschema;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.adapter.NonNegativeIntegerAdapter;
009import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.adapter.PositiveIntegerAdapter;
010import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.adapter.StringAdapter;
011import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.adapter.TokenAdapter;
012import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.markup.MarkupLine;
013import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.markup.MarkupLineAdapter;
014import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.IBoundObject;
015import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.IMetaschemaData;
016import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.JsonGroupAsBehavior;
017import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.constraint.IConstraint;
018import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.util.ObjectUtils;
019import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.BoundAssembly;
020import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.BoundField;
021import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.BoundFlag;
022import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.GroupAs;
023import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.Matches;
024import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.MetaschemaAssembly;
025import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.ValueConstraints;
026
027import org.apache.commons.lang3.builder.ReflectionToStringBuilder;
028import org.apache.commons.lang3.builder.ToStringStyle;
029
030import java.math.BigInteger;
031import java.util.LinkedList;
032import java.util.List;
033
034@SuppressWarnings({
035    "PMD.DataClass",
036    "PMD.FieldNamingConventions"
037})
038@MetaschemaAssembly(
039    formalName = "Assembly Reference",
040    name = "assembly-reference",
041    moduleClass = MetaschemaModelModule.class)
042public class AssemblyReference implements IBoundObject {
043  private final IMetaschemaData __metaschemaData;
044
045  @BoundFlag(
046      formalName = "Global Assembly Reference",
047      name = "ref",
048      required = true,
049      typeAdapter = TokenAdapter.class)
050  private String _ref;
051
052  @BoundFlag(
053      formalName = "Assembly Reference Binary Name",
054      name = "index",
055      typeAdapter = PositiveIntegerAdapter.class)
056  private BigInteger _index;
057
058  @BoundFlag(
059      formalName = "Deprecated Version",
060      name = "deprecated",
061      typeAdapter = StringAdapter.class)
062  private String _deprecated;
063
064  @BoundFlag(
065      formalName = "Minimum Occurrence",
066      name = "min-occurs",
067      defaultValue = "0",
068      typeAdapter = NonNegativeIntegerAdapter.class)
069  private BigInteger _minOccurs;
070
071  @BoundFlag(
072      formalName = "Maximum Occurrence",
073      name = "max-occurs",
074      defaultValue = "1",
075      typeAdapter = StringAdapter.class,
076      valueConstraints = @ValueConstraints(
077          matches = @Matches(level = IConstraint.Level.ERROR, pattern = "^[1-9][0-9]*|unbounded$")))
078  private String _maxOccurs;
079
080  @BoundField(
081      formalName = "Formal Name",
082      description = "A formal name for the data construct, to be presented in documentation.",
083      useName = "formal-name")
084  private String _formalName;
085
086  @BoundField(
087      formalName = "Description",
088      description = "A short description of the data construct's purpose, describing the constructs semantics.",
089      useName = "description",
090      typeAdapter = MarkupLineAdapter.class)
091  private MarkupLine _description;
092
093  @BoundAssembly(
094      formalName = "Property",
095      useName = "prop",
096      maxOccurs = -1,
097      groupAs = @GroupAs(name = "props", inJson = JsonGroupAsBehavior.LIST))
098  private List<Property> _props;
099
100  @BoundField(
101      formalName = "Use Name",
102      description = "Allows the name of the definition to be overridden.",
103      useName = "use-name")
104  private UseName _useName;
105
106  @BoundAssembly(
107      formalName = "Group As",
108      useName = "group-as")
109  private GroupingAs _groupAs;
110
111  @BoundField(
112      formalName = "Remarks",
113      description = "Any explanatory or helpful information to be provided about the remarks parent.",
114      useName = "remarks")
115  private Remarks _remarks;
116
117  public AssemblyReference() {
118    this(null);
119  }
120
121  public AssemblyReference(IMetaschemaData data) {
122    this.__metaschemaData = data;
123  }
124
125  @Override
126  public IMetaschemaData getMetaschemaData() {
127    return __metaschemaData;
128  }
129
130  public String getRef() {
131    return _ref;
132  }
133
134  public void setRef(String value) {
135    _ref = value;
136  }
137
138  public BigInteger getIndex() {
139    return _index;
140  }
141
142  public void setIndex(BigInteger value) {
143    _index = value;
144  }
145
146  public String getDeprecated() {
147    return _deprecated;
148  }
149
150  public void setDeprecated(String value) {
151    _deprecated = value;
152  }
153
154  public BigInteger getMinOccurs() {
155    return _minOccurs;
156  }
157
158  public void setMinOccurs(BigInteger value) {
159    _minOccurs = value;
160  }
161
162  public String getMaxOccurs() {
163    return _maxOccurs;
164  }
165
166  public void setMaxOccurs(String value) {
167    _maxOccurs = value;
168  }
169
170  public String getFormalName() {
171    return _formalName;
172  }
173
174  public void setFormalName(String value) {
175    _formalName = value;
176  }
177
178  public MarkupLine getDescription() {
179    return _description;
180  }
181
182  public void setDescription(MarkupLine value) {
183    _description = value;
184  }
185
186  public List<Property> getProps() {
187    return _props;
188  }
189
190  public void setProps(List<Property> value) {
191    _props = value;
192  }
193
194  /**
195   * Add a new {@link Property} item to the underlying collection.
196   *
197   * @param item
198   *          the item to add
199   * @return {@code true}
200   */
201  public boolean addProp(Property item) {
202    Property value = ObjectUtils.requireNonNull(item, "item cannot be null");
203    if (_props == null) {
204      _props = new LinkedList<>();
205    }
206    return _props.add(value);
207  }
208
209  /**
210   * Remove the first matching {@link Property} item from the underlying
211   * collection.
212   *
213   * @param item
214   *          the item to remove
215   * @return {@code true} if the item was removed or {@code false} otherwise
216   */
217  public boolean removeProp(Property item) {
218    Property value = ObjectUtils.requireNonNull(item, "item cannot be null");
219    return _props != null && _props.remove(value);
220  }
221
222  public UseName getUseName() {
223    return _useName;
224  }
225
226  public void setUseName(UseName value) {
227    _useName = value;
228  }
229
230  public GroupingAs getGroupAs() {
231    return _groupAs;
232  }
233
234  public void setGroupAs(GroupingAs value) {
235    _groupAs = value;
236  }
237
238  public Remarks getRemarks() {
239    return _remarks;
240  }
241
242  public void setRemarks(Remarks value) {
243    _remarks = value;
244  }
245
246  @Override
247  public String toString() {
248    return new ReflectionToStringBuilder(this, ToStringStyle.MULTI_LINE_STYLE).toString();
249  }
250}
